welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Sussex, where charming small-town vibes and scenic landscapes await you! Known for its rich history and delicious seafood, we invite you to explore and discover all that our beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lawrence J Timmerman Airport is a small but efficient space, providing all necessary amenities for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at West Bend Airport handles all commercial flights and is equipped with modern amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at West Bend Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at General Mitchell International Airport handles all domestic and international flights. It offers a variety of dining and shopping options for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C is primarily used by Southwest Airlines and offers a variety of amenities for passengers including restaurants, shops, and charging stations.

terminals.name: Concourse D
terminals.description: Concourse D is used by Delta Air Lines and also offers a variety of amenities for passengers such as restaurants, shops, and a Delta Sky Club lounge.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free Wi-Fi network by selecting 'MKE Free Wi-Fi' from their device's list of available networks.
